title: Tour Today! 8 Weeks Free at Murphy Station Apartments
posting_body: ['Murphy Station Apartments', '1008 E El Camino Real, Sunnyvale, CA, 94087', "Sunnyvale's premier living destination", 'Welcome to Murphy Station Apartments.', 'Our stylish luxury apartments offer spacious floor plans and an array of amazing amenities and wonderful features.', "Within each of our lovely apartment homes, you'll find an alluring balance of design and convenience.", 'SPECIAL PROMOTION:', '8 Weeks Free and a Look and Lease bonus of $1,000 Amazon Gift card', 'Details', 'Availability: Two Bedrooms ($4,600 - $5,550) (1,047-1,249 sqft)', 'Utilities: Water, Trash, Sewer, and Gas included in rent', 'Laundry: W/D Inside Unit', 'Pet Friendly: Cats, Dogs (75lb weight restrictions, call office for breed restrictions)', 'Pet Deposit: $500 Standard', 'Pet rent: $50/month', 'Amenities', 'Expansive Pool & Spa', "Scenic rooftop deck with outdoor seating, BBQ grill, and Tv's", 'Spacious clubroom lounge', 'State of the art fitness center and yoga room', 'Beautiful courtyard with BBQ grill', 'We-work and Tech lounge', 'Outdoor game lawn', 'Pet spa', 'Features', 'Stainless Steel Whirlpool Appliances', 'Gas Ranges', 'Quartz countertop', 'Balcony/patio', 'Central Heat/AC', 'Cable-ready', 'Controlled access; Stairs, Elevators', 'Parking garage with available Electric car charging stations', 'Flexible touring options available by appointment.', 'Call us today for more information.', 'show contact info', 'You may also visit our website at <URL>', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Tuesday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Wednesday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Thursday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Friday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Saturday:', '8am - 5pm', 'Sunday:', '8am - 5pm']
